snippet.title: Lunars - The Ultimate Zodiac Party Game!
snippet.description:
Lunars, get set, GO! 🐀🐂🐅🐇🐉🐍🐎🐑🐒🐓🐕🐖

Get ready for the ultimate zodiac party game!🎉🥳🌙

Play as your favourite Zodiac and compete across unique game boards on a mini-game fuelled party with up to 8 friends to win first place in the Lunar race. Chase geese in a mall, swim in a hot pot, recruit hungry penguins and more in some of the crazy mini-games on this adventure.

Wishlist Now on Steam!  store.steampowered.com/app/1031080/Lunars
